metadata.name: Muse
metadata.description:
This work is the first of this collection and my very first work on this platform.

Format: 5504 x 6880 pixels

The photo was originally taken with a Zenit analog film camera, which is over 50 years old. After the photo was digitized and uploaded to the platform.

Harmony and positive energy is exactly what I associate with this place. These are the emotions I feel when I remember those moments and those people.
